reviews.text:
Waffle, Butter, (Maple) Syrup - that's what I get here. Overall it's a bit mild but that doesn't keep me from vaping this. I never liked FW Butterscotch Ripple that much but at 1.25% it just works and it's giving me more of a syrupy sensation.&#xD;
&#xD;
To me it's something I can vape all day without being bored and that's not an easy achievement.
